    public class Icicle
extends org.bukkit.plugin.java.JavaPlugin
    This class doesn't really have functions, only update checkers. All methods/utils in Icicle should be used with static access or with the provided constructors! Only purpose is version checking and providing methods in Classloader without shading. Also contains metadata information!

    1.0.0-SNAPSHOT
